Abell Pest Control is a family owned Canadian company dedicated to providing effective, professional and courteous service in pest management. Started in 1924 with one office, Abell now employs several hundred people with branch offices across Canada and the United States.

Guaranteed Pest Control in Canada

Control of mice, roaches, ants, wasps, animals and dozens of other pests
-Full money-back guarantee
-FREE no-obligation quote
-Effective, safe and fast pest elimination

Guaranteed Pest Control
Pests bring dirt, disease, and discomfort through their bites and droppings. Effective, safe and fast elimination of the pest is what you need now.

Fast & Safe Elimination
Controlling pests can be done safely and effectively by a trained professional. Effective pest control is a three-step process:

1)-Identification: Our pest control technician will review your property to find the nature and extent of the pest infestation. The most important element is locating the source of the infestation.
2)-Elimination: Once the pests have been identified and located, your technician will safely eliminate the infestation -- guaranteed*.
3)-Prevention: After the pest infestation is eliminated, your technician will provide you with a complete review of your property, making specific recommendations to help keep the pests away permanently.


Guaranteed Extermination
Your contractual pest is Gone and Guaranteed. If you are not satisfied with the services provided to you within the guarantee period, you will receive a Full Money Back Refund!

* All Abell Service Recommendations must be complied with and follow up services allowed for during the guarantee period to be eligible for any refund. Call for details.

Having a Bedbugs issue?

We’re not gonna lie, getting rid of bedbugs is quite a challenge! With the heat, it’s over once and for all!

•	You can return to the comfort of your home the same day! Safe for people and pets!

We are also active members of some of the largest pest management associations, including NPMA (National Pest Management Association), CPMA (Canadian Pest Management Association) and OPCA (Ontario Pest Control Association).

Essen Pest Control is a trustworthy name in domestic and commercial pest control for over 15 years. We are based in Toronto and Ottawa but cater to your needs around the GTA and Ottawa, seven days a week. We are government approved, licensed, insured and bonded pest control company.
 
We are fully trained and experienced professionals that attend to your needs effectively. We identify a problem quickly and deploy solutions just as quick. Our goal is to provide quality service and affordable pricing while protecting our customers from unwanted pests. We are proud to provide the best pest control service the first time and every time. The cost of professional pest control service can often be less than you would spend trying to solve a problem yourself. If the job is not done properly, money spent is often a waste.
 
There are also times when you owners aggravate the problem which may further increase costs of solution. Although there are a number of over-the-counter products available for pest control, its success rate greatly depends on a number of factors that we, the professionals know.
 
Indiscriminate spraying can be harmful for your families, therefore it is highly recommended to depend on us, rather than make this a weekend project for you. Improper pesticide use may eliminate symptoms but not the real cause of a problem. We make sure that the problem is eliminated from the root. 

And quite frankly, if you are not sure about what to do and if you conclude that the problem is more than you can handle yourself.

profile:
Get 'Em Out Wildlife Control Inc. is Ottawa's ONLY full restoration company specifically designed for pest control, to give business and homeowners a permanent solution to their urban wildlife problems. 

Trapping and relocating animals is NOT a permanent solution, and if not done correctly can cause severe stress and be fatal to the animal. Moving animals farther than a kilometer away in most cases may result in heavy fines or result in criminal charges. 

Get 'Em Out Wildlife Control will identify all entry and re-entry points on your home or business. This detailed process ensures a permanent solution can be offered. Once the main entry points are located a one-way-door will be installed allowing the animals to safely leave the building. All identified re-entry points will be secured against re-entry. Any damages caused to the building or structure will be fully repaired (shingles, fascia, soffit, siding, insulation, etc.). 

All workmanship and materials comes with a full lifetime guarantee to all serviced area by Get 'Em Out Wildlife Control. 

We specialize in Mice, Squirrels, Skunks, Bats, Raccoons and full restoration and repairs.

For booking please visit WWW.GETEMOUTWILDLIFE.COM or email SERVICE@GETEMOUTWILDLIFE.COM and one of our urban wildlife specialist will get back to you quickly.
